oke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-log-in ml-2 h-3.5 w-3.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m10 17 5-5-5-5\"></path><path d=\"M15 12H3\"></path><path d=\"M15 3h4a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v14a2 2 0 0 1-2 2h-4\"></path></svg>تسجيل الدخول</a></div><button type=\"button\" class=\"landing-mobile-trigger h-11 w-11 justify-self-end place-items-center rounded-lg bg-white text-navy shadow-[0_10px_22px_rgb(24_23_21/0.08)] transition hover:bg-[#fff7ea] hover:text-gold\" aria-label=\"فتح القائمة\" aria-expanded=\"false\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-menu h-5 w-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M4 5h16\"></path><path d=\"M4 12h16\"></path><path d=\"M4 19h16\"></path></svg></button></div></div></header><main><section class=\"section-compact\"><div class=\"container-page\"><div class=\"grid items-center gap-8 lg:grid-cols-[1.08fr_0.92fr]\"><div class=\"relative min-h-[440px] overflow-hidden\"><img alt=\"مبنى عقاري مؤسسي\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-contain object-left-bottom\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"55vw\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhero-full-cover.png&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhero-full-cover.png&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhero-full-cover.png&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhero-full-cover.png&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhero-full-cover.png&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhero-full-cover.png&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhero-full-cover.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhero-full-cover.png&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhero-full-cover.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhero-full-cover.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/></div><div class=\"text-right\"><p class=\"mb-3 text-sm font-extrabold text-[#A7815E]\">من مهابة</p><h1 class=\"font-display text-[clamp(2.1rem,4.2vw,4.35rem)] font-black leading-[1.34] text-[#1D1916]\">نحول الأصول العقارية إلى<span class=\"block text-[#A7815E]\">مساهمات عقارية منظمة</span>وفق أعلى معايير الحوكمة والشفافية والامتثال.</h1><p class=\"mt-5 max-w-2xl text-base font-bold leading-9 text-muted\">نساعد ملاك الأصول العقارية على دراسة أصولهم وهيكلتها وتحويلها إلى مساهمات عقارية منظمة عبر منظومة متكاملة من الخدمات والشركاء والحوكمة.</p></div></div><div class=\"mt-8 grid gap-4 rounded-lg border border-line bg-white/62 p-4 md:grid-cols-3\"><article class=\"rounded-lg border border-line bg-white/72 p-5 text-center shadow-[0_10px_24px_rgb(29_25_22/0.035)]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-eye mx-auto h-10 w-10 stroke-[1.5] text-[#A7815E]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M2.062 12.348a1 1 0 0 1 0-.696 10.75 10.75 0 0 1 19.876 0 1 1 0 0 1 0 .696 10.75 10.75 0 0 1-19.876 0\"></path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"3\"></circle></svg><h3 class=\"mt-3 font-display text-xl font-extrabold text-[#1D1916]\">الرؤية</h3><p class=\"mx-auto mt-2 max-w-xs text-sm font-bold leading-8 text-muted\">أن تكون مهابة المنصة الرائدة في تحويل الأصول العقارية إلى مساهمات عقارية منظمة.</p></article><article class=\"rounded-lg border border-line bg-white/72 p-5 text-center shadow-[0_10px_24px_rgb(29_25_22/0.035)]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-target mx-auto h-10 w-10 stroke-[1.5] text-[#A7815E]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"6\"></circle><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"2\"></circle></svg><h3 class=\"mt-3 font-display text-xl font-extrabold text-[#1D1916]\">الرسالة</h3><p class=\"mx-auto mt-2 max-w-xs text-sm font-bold leading-8 text-muted\">تمكين ملاك الأصول العقارية من تعظيم قيمة أصولهم وفق أعلى معايير الحوكمة والشفافية والامتثال.</p></article><article class=\"rounded-lg border border-line bg-white/72 p-5 text-center shadow-[0_10px_24px_rgb(29_25_22/0.035)]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-gem mx-auto h-10 w-10 stroke-[1.5] text-[#A7815E]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10.5 3 8 9l4 13 4-13-2.5-6\"></path><path d=\"M17 3a2 2 0 0 1 1.6.8l3 4a2 2 0 0 1 .013 2.382l-7.99 10.986a2 2 0 0 1-3.247 0l-7.99-10.986A2 2 0 0 1 2.4 7.8l2.998-3.997A2 2 0 0 1 7 3z\"></path><path d=\"M2 9h20\"></path></svg><h3 class=\"mt-3 font-display text-xl font-extrabold text-[#1D1916]\">القيم</h3><p class=\"mx-auto mt-2 max-w-xs text-sm font-bold leading-8 text-muted\">الشفافية، الحوكمة، الامتثال، الابتكار، الاستدامة.</p></article></div></div></section><section class=\"section-compact\"><div class=\"container-page\"><h2 class=\"mb-5 text-center font-display text-3xl font-extrabold text-[#1D1916] gold-divider\">ماذا تقدم مهابة؟</h2><div class=\"grid gap-3 md:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-6\"><article class=\"rounded-lg border border-line bg-white/72 p-5 text-center shadow-[0_10px_24px_rgb(29_25_22/0.035)]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-building2 lucide-building-2 mx-auto h-10 w-10 stroke-[1.5] text-[#A7815E]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 12h4\"></path><path d=\"M1